even Tcl if we could get the graphics device issues ironed out (or did
we already do that? How portable is the tkrplot stuff?).

For my part it is a major issue how the internal programmability (i.e.
writing GUI elements in R) pans out. I still haven't seen anything
that matches Tcl/Tk in that respect.

